Clinical data

Source: R/data.R
traitData.Rd

Metadata containing the variable to predict

Usage

traitData

Format

Matrix with samples as rows and target variable as column

Source

Mariathasan et al. (2018), doi: https://doi.org/10.1038/nature25501

Examples

data(traitData)
